sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as RagasEvaluatorInline
    participant InfAPI as Inference API<br/>(in-process)
    participant DataIO as DatasetIO API<br/>(in-process)
    participant Remote as RagasEvaluatorRemote
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pipeline Pod
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,DataIO: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation (Synchronous)
        Client->>LLS: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>(HTTP 8321)
        LLS->>Inline: delegate to inline provider
        Inline->>DataIO: get_dataset(dataset_id)<br/>(in-process)
        DataIO-->>Inline: dataset rows
        loop For each metric (answer_relevancy, faithfulness, etc.)
            Inline->>InfAPI: LLM completion<br/>(in-process, max_workers=1)
            InfAPI-->>Inline: completion result
            Inline->>InfAPI: embedding generation<br/>(in-process)
            InfAPI-->>Inline: embeddings
        end
        Inline-->>LLS: EvaluateResponse
        LLS-->>Client: JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Asynchronous via Kubeflow Pipelines)
        Client->>LLS: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>(HTTP 8321)
        LLS->>Remote: delegate to remote provider
        Remote->>KFP: GET /healthz<br/>(HTTPS 443, Bearer Token)
        KFP-->>Remote: healthy
        Remote->>KFP: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>(HTTPS 443, Bearer Token)
        KFP-->>Remote: run_id
        Remote-->>LLS: job_id
        LLS-->>Client: Job submitted (job_id)

        Note over KFPPod,S3: Pipeline execution (async)
        KFP->>KFPPod: Start pipeline
        KFPPod->>LLS: GET datasets<br/>(HTTP 8321)
        LLS-->>KFPPod: dataset rows
        KFPPod->>LLS: POST completions + embeddings<br/>(HTTP 8321)
        LLS-->>KFPPod: inference results
        KFPPod->>S3: PUT results.jsonl<br/>(HTTPS 443, AWS IAM)

        Note over Client,S3: Status polling
        Client->>LLS: GET /eval/job_status(job_id)<br/>(HTTP 8321)
        LLS->>Remote: check status
        Remote->>KFP: GET /apis/v2beta1/runs/{id}<br/>(HTTPS 443, Bearer Token)
        KFP-->>Remote: run status
        Remote-->>LLS: status
        LLS-->>Client: status response

        Note over Client,S3: Result retrieval
        Client->>LLS: GET /eval/job_result(job_id)<br/>(HTTP 8321)
        LLS->>Remote: get result
        Remote->>S3: GET results.jsonl<br/>(HTTPS 443, AWS IAM)
        S3-->>Remote: evaluation results
        Remote-->>LLS: EvaluateResponse
        LLS-->>Client: JSON response
    end
